{"tid":93224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗唔畀上機，夫婦將牠遺棄室外凍死","createTime":"2017-01-24T08:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T09:55:24.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78350fe475a2b6b0c2f5e282513c898522cceeb9","tid":93224,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:59:15.000Z","msg":"夫婦登機前被告知不能帶「Tori」上機，&hellip;&hellip;丈夫竟帶「Tori」走出機場客運大樓，並把牠遺棄室外，之後若無其事般與太太上機。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n夫婦抵達目的地後，向漢堡警方報案指「Tori」失蹤3天<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n機場人員最終在一處人煙罕至的地點發現「Tori」的遺體，機場發言人表示，「無法相信一個人會對狗狗做出這樣的事」，又痛斥兩人未有向機場求助，否則狗狗或可獲救。"},{"pid":"f68ba84e1746511071b1fc29093b4e17c94f223b","tid":93224,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170124/large/1485229764_a247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170124%2Flarge%2F1485229764_a247.jpg&h=f98597ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d7a06f01c7c77f829f9776f868436ab1c1bddf8","tid":93224,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:00:59.000Z","msg":"都估到係垃圾國家 俄狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6976591b80b69e750877233a6055d9661173dc2","tid":93224,"uid":61044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:01:40.000Z","msg":"死左寶落地獄"},{"pid":"30e57a6d303432b3890e220501c0c446a0851901","tid":93224,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"真係慘<br />\n臨死果刻 都等緊自己&quot;信任的主人&quot;返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2462362721167fd9cfbdfa62adbe819e5864df98","tid":93224,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:08:12.000Z","msg":